               <p>314. 
               
                  <persName id="t17960406-85-defend946" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     BATES
                  <interp inst="t17960406-85-defend946" type="surname" value="BATES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-defend946" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-defend946" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-defend946" type="age" value="32"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17960406-85-off479" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-off479" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-off479" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960406-85-cd480" type="crimeDate">19th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-85-off479 t17960406-85-cd480"></join>, a musical instrument called a piano forte, value 10l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960406-85-victim948" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Longman
                  <interp inst="t17960406-85-victim948" type="surname" value="Longman"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-victim948" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-victim948" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             and 
               <persName id="t17960406-85-victim949" type="victimName">
                  Francis Fane 
                  Broderip
               <interp inst="t17960406-85-victim949" type="surname" value="Broderip"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-victim949" type="given" value="Francis Fane"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-victim949" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Second Count. Laying it to be the property of 
               <persName id="t17960406-85-victim950" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Blake
               <interp inst="t17960406-85-victim950" type="surname" value="Blake"></interp>
