                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-85-defend946 t17960406-85-punish483"></join>
               Confined twelve months in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17960406-85-punish484" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-punish484" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960406-85-punish484" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-85-defend946 t17960406-85-punish484"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERGEANT.</p>
